{"tid":328494,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人拍完長拖散左之後覺得付出好累","createTime":"2017-07-19T15:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T05:05:03.000Z","uid":75964,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e68ec8c57337e02508c46be65f501a8edf133f68","tid":328494,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:21:31.000Z","msg":"之前拍左3年幾散左，<br />\n到依家拍緊拖，但覺得不斷付出好累，<br />\n好驚做完100分女朋友最尾都係會俾人掉低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n份人好無安全感，好驚佢出去偷食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有好多既習慣又要重新磨合<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有同樣感覺？要點樣解決無勇氣再愛嘅毛病？"},{"pid":"928431a2e06703946c44656a0f5b4a1160287194","tid":328494,"uid":79387,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"真絲 同感 <br />\n好難再信人"},{"pid":"1692d7a6a28d19d4d16260da71e44ddc896effde","tid":328494,"uid":75964,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真絲 同感 <br />\n好難再信人</blockquote><br />\n自問上一段關係都好俾心機維繫<br />\n但都走唔到最後<br />\n我都係想簡簡單單大家對大家好 又好驚最尾會受傷"},{"pid":"d930c43f38b051e9c6479ea4d4575b33f464736a","tid":328494,"uid":73069,"like":5,"dislike":52,"score":-47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:30:43.000Z","msg":"10個男人9個貪新忘舊 除非你男朋友係一個毒撚<br />\n男人偷食天經地義 只係證明你無能力mark住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32f1988daf3849abb5a73832d8c42ce40cf6abb","tid":328494,"uid":58119,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:31:37.000Z","msg":"唔敢再付出全部嘅愛 真係好驚好驚突然佢就同你講冇哂feel"},{"pid":"010c9ba56b1134e759aa73336661716e72051cb7","tid":328494,"uid":5806,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10個男人9個貪新忘舊 除非你男朋友係一個毒撚<br />\n男人偷食天經地義 只係證明你無能力mark住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估女人唔會貪新忘舊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人夠會偷食㗎啦<br />\n根本冇話男人定女人 呢啲野好睇人"},{"pid":"12efd654aaa1269dfda39e13c5b5599429864dac","tid":328494,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"信心真係好緊要 <br />\n無信好難一齊行得耐"},{"pid":"510f9d1fd06642c291a7737c8cf4cbcae0806f73","tid":328494,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔敢再付出全部嘅愛 真係好驚好驚突然佢就同你講冇哂feel</blockquote><br />\n所謂嘅冇feel咪即係冇新鮮感同埋唔愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再唔係咪鐘意另一知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faaa9a7be28ad76009327473ee97645b1b12ec2c","tid":328494,"uid":119248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"係⋯怕面對新感情又要重新再去悉應一個人<br />\n你唔知同佢會點⋯會唔會有將來<br />\n好似又好多不穩定因素⋯好唔安心咁"},{"pid":"b1a2931631d313b70aa2e6b84d8334f02ceb9ebb","tid":328494,"uid":117187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:36:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔敢再付出全部嘅愛 真係<span style=\"color: red;\">好驚好驚突然佢就同你講冇哂fee</span>l</blockquote><br />\n呢個真<br />\n利申︰拍過四年散左"},{"pid":"4728d80eac366ebd965b2a87d66d06872d04774c","tid":328494,"uid":29789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:37:15.000Z","msg":"我兩年幾散左<br />\n以為自己俾多D空間/自由佢 佢就當你唔緊佢<br />\n唔係話自己完全無做錯過 但互相體諒 了解對方為自己付出過D咩 我覺得好重要<br />\n可能唔關你講嘅野 純粹想紓發下<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2da0bd52f01136a1836414d7c61c2c848bf3be","tid":328494,"uid":75964,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>10個男人9個貪新忘舊 除非你男朋友係一個毒撚<br />\n男人偷食天經地義 只係證明你無能力mark住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能我份人比較守舊掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得某程度上拍拖係一種責任黎<br />\n你決定左同佢一齊 就要專一 唔好因為做啲咩野而傷害左對方<br />\n因為發現人地偷食個心真係會好傷架（我係過來人）"},{"pid":"45eb9061ee4b5f57f4e4925168901c8e71ec2bb6","tid":328494,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係⋯怕面對新感情又要重新再去悉應一個人<br />\n你唔知同佢會點⋯會唔會有將來<br />\n好似又好多不穩定因素⋯好唔安心咁</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好驚拍多兩三年又係咩都無<br />\n我都想自己secure啲架"},{"pid":"d9ea0eff0023ceab369848a064a48bc428b39ad4","tid":328494,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:41:02.000Z","msg":"拍左4年無左<br />\n無力無心情再去重新了解另一個人"},{"pid":"88279957e2fcd5d9fc22fc7d363a732c0956612d","tid":328494,"uid":49561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"覺得要重新認識了解一個人／被人了解好煩<br />\n同埋冇以前咁想毫無保留付出所有 冇咁上心<br />\n但其實而家男朋友好愛我對我超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159222d251dc2ba2d8f9d40692b9dd1ab35d179f","tid":328494,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得要重新認識了解一個人／被人了解好煩<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋冇以前咁想毫無保留付出所有 冇咁上心</span><br />\n但其實而家男朋友好愛我對我超好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nI know that feel sis"},{"pid":"63629e40ca67e14f06dd6f8941cb60651dc923de","tid":328494,"uid":75964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拍左4年無左<br />\n無力無心情再去重新了解另一個人</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 我唔明點解我ex可以咁快搵到個新既一齊"},{"pid":"dc56124a75cb192d0a652f4d5bd939fd5712c532","tid":328494,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍左4年無左<br />\n無力無心情再去重新了解另一個人</blockquote><br />\n岩呀 我唔明點解我ex可以咁快搵到個新既一齊</blockquote><br />\n我明<br />\n為自己好 斷絕所有來往啦"},{"pid":"7083e7a428ad8ba48ab3cadb73dd1dfb59f11182","tid":328494,"uid":4728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7911999be1f576ee0b499120c88285407ec3657","tid":328494,"uid